    "org_about":  "educations.com is the global online meeting point for students and schools in over 210 countries. There, prospective students can quickly and easily find relevant information on study abroad options, while schools and higher education institutions can market themselves effectively to the right audience.",
    "en":  {
               "lang":  "en",
               "title":  "Study in Germany 2026: A Unique Opportunity for Gulf Students, Graduate and Join Europe’s Strongest Job Market",
               "sections":  [
                                {
                                    "header":  "Opportunity description",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1595\" data-start=\"1310\"\u003eGermany is one of the world\u0026rsquo;s top study destinations, offering high-quality education, affordable costs, and strong career opportunities after graduation. German universities provide a wide range of English-taught programs across engineering, business, technology, and creative fields.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1652\" data-start=\"1597\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThis opportunity highlights top institutions including:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003col class=\"kh\" data-end=\"1777\" data-start=\"1653\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1677\" data-section-id=\"pbkxzp\" data-start=\"1653\"\u003eRWTH Aachen University\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1694\" data-section-id=\"gervyd\" data-start=\"1678\"\u003eSRH University\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1733\" data-section-id=\"1wvkbnh\" data-start=\"1695\"\u003eFulda University of Applied Sciences\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1777\" data-section-id=\"zj1bxg\" data-start=\"1734\"\u003eUniversity of Europe for Applied Sciences\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1779\"\u003eThese universities are known for their practical approach, strong industry connections, and international learning environments. Ideal for students seeking high-quality education, global exposure, and strong career prospects in Europe.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-18\" data-turn=\"assistant\" data-turn-id=\"request-WEB:8b9c3026-ae85-47f6-b8e7-0b955243f931-9\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"eb827903-e339-4498-9f0c-39ce7346cadf\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-3-instant\" data-turn-start-message=\"true\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"0\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"123\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eStart applying now to available programs at German universities: \u003ca href=\"https://www.educations.com/highlights/study-in-germany?utm_source=for9a\u0026utm_medium=paid+partner\u0026utm_campaign=Channel+Partner-2026+Study+in+Germany+School+Campaign+Q2\u0026utm_id=Channel+Partner-2026+Study+in+Germany+School+Campaign+Q2\"\u003ea wide range of options to suit different fields of study.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"3595\" data-start=\"3579\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTuition Fees:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e-Public universities (e.g., Fulda): low or minimal tuition fees\u003cbr\u003e-Private universities (SRH, UE): tuition varies by program\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"3738\" data-start=\"3722\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eScholarships:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e-Opportunities such as DAAD scholarships\u003cbr\u003e-Partial scholarships or discounts offered by some universities\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"1652\" data-start=\"1597\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eِTop institutions:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1779\"\u003e1.RWTH Aachen University\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1779\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://images.for9a.com/thumb/max-720-auto-90-webp/t/70213-rwth-aachen-university.jfif\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" data-sizes=\"[object Object]\" data-original=\"[object Object]\" data-name=\"70213-rwth-aachen-university.jfif\" data-src=\"[object Object]\"\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"449\" data-start=\"275\"\u003eRWTH Aachen University is one of Europe\u0026rsquo;s leading technical universities, making it a top choice for students aiming to \u003cstrong data-end=\"448\" data-start=\"395\"\u003estudy abroad in engineering and technology fields\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4 data-end=\"480\" data-section-id=\"15veiqz\" data-start=\"451\"\u003eWhy choose RWTH Aachen?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"720\" data-start=\"481\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"525\" data-section-id=\"1jua15t\" data-start=\"481\"\u003eGlobally recognized technical university\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"583\" data-section-id=\"160xd00\" data-start=\"526\"\u003eStrong focus on engineering, innovation, and research\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"628\" data-section-id=\"1lp1ouc\" data-start=\"584\"\u003eClose partnerships with major industries\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"672\" data-section-id=\"w3pbes\" data-start=\"629\"\u003eHighly competitive academic environment\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"720\" data-section-id=\"1nxnahp\" data-start=\"673\"\u003eExcellent career prospects after graduation\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"805\" data-start=\"722\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"738\" data-start=\"725\"\u003eBest for:\u003c/strong\u003e High-achieving students targeting engineering and research careers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"805\" data-start=\"722\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"805\" data-start=\"722\"\u003e2.SRH University\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"805\" data-start=\"722\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://images.for9a.com/thumb/max-720-auto-90-webp/t/67488-srh-university.jfif\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" data-sizes=\"[object Object]\" data-original=\"[object Object]\" data-name=\"67488-srh-university.jfif\" data-src=\"[object Object]\"\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1021\" data-start=\"875\"\u003eSRH University offers a modern and flexible approach to \u003cstrong data-end=\"950\" data-start=\"931\"\u003estudying abroad\u003c/strong\u003e, with a strong emphasis on practical skills and real-world experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4 data-end=\"1044\" data-section-id=\"16f2whn\" data-start=\"1023\"\u003eWhy choose SRH?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"1248\" data-start=\"1045\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1072\" data-section-id=\"67bhm3\" data-start=\"1045\"\u003eEnglish-taught programs\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1120\" data-section-id=\"cc8esd\" data-start=\"1073\"\u003eUnique CORE learning model (practice-based)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1175\" data-section-id=\"1mq5l9x\" data-start=\"1121\"\u003eFlexible study formats (on-campus, online, hybrid)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1213\" data-section-id=\"hauka6\" data-start=\"1176\"\u003eInternational student environment\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1248\" data-section-id=\"onhjlg\" data-start=\"1214\"\u003eStrong academic support system\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1327\" data-start=\"1250\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"1266\" data-start=\"1253\"\u003eBest for:\u003c/strong\u003e Students seeking flexibility, hands-on learning, and support.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1779\"\u003e3.Fulda University of Applied Sciences\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1779\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://images.for9a.com/thumb/max-720-auto-90-webp/t/36254-fulda-university-of-applied-sciences.jfif\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" data-sizes=\"[object Object]\" data-original=\"[object Object]\" data-name=\"36254-fulda-university-of-applied-sciences.jfif\" data-src=\"[object Object]\"\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1557\" data-start=\"1419\"\u003eFulda University is an excellent option for students looking to \u003cstrong data-end=\"1524\" data-start=\"1483\"\u003estudy abroad in Germany at a low cost\u003c/strong\u003e without compromising on quality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4 data-end=\"1582\" data-section-id=\"bu6fjc\" data-start=\"1559\"\u003eWhy choose Fulda?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"1810\" data-start=\"1583\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1632\" data-section-id=\"18rv45i\" data-start=\"1583\"\u003ePublic university with low or no tuition fees\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1663\" data-section-id=\"1tnj9n7\" data-start=\"1633\"\u003ePractice-oriented programs\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1711\" data-section-id=\"1ltwmkf\" data-start=\"1664\"\u003eSupportive and smaller learning environment\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1757\" data-section-id=\"11ygejw\" data-start=\"1712\"\u003eGrowing number of English-taught programs\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1810\" data-section-id=\"x2unvx\" data-start=\"1758\"\u003eAccess to scholarship opportunities (e.g., DAAD)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"1880\" data-start=\"1812\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"1828\" data-start=\"1815\"\u003eBest for:\u003c/strong\u003e Budget-conscious students seeking quality education.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1880\" data-start=\"1812\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e4.University of Europe for Applied Sciences (UE)\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1880\" data-start=\"1812\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://images.for9a.com/thumb/max-720-auto-90-webp/t/50904-6-university-of-europe-innovation-hub-germany.webp\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib fr-fil\" data-sizes=\"[object Object]\" data-original=\"[object Object]\" data-name=\"50904-6-university-of-europe-innovation-hub-germany.webp\" data-src=\"[object Object]\"\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"2160\" data-start=\"1982\"\u003eThe University of Europe for Applied Sciences offers career-focused programs ideal for students interested in \u003cstrong data-end=\"2159\" data-start=\"2092\"\u003ebusiness, technology, and creative fields while studying abroad\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4 data-end=\"2182\" data-section-id=\"ii6hmq\" data-start=\"2162\"\u003eWhy choose UE?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"2440\" data-start=\"2183\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2232\" data-section-id=\"egadku\" data-start=\"2183\"\u003eStrong programs in business, tech, and design\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2284\" data-section-id=\"ovahx\" data-start=\"2233\"\u003eEnglish-taught, internationally focused degrees\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2339\" data-section-id=\"owtnol\" data-start=\"2285\"\u003eEmphasis on employability and industry connections\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2393\" data-section-id=\"5tgk0g\" data-start=\"2340\"\u003eModern campuses in major cities (Berlin, Hamburg)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2440\" data-section-id=\"1ul9d9d\" data-start=\"2394\"\u003eSmall class sizes and personalized support\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"2526\" data-start=\"2442\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"2458\" data-start=\"2445\"\u003eBest for:\u003c/strong\u003e Students seeking a modern, international, career-oriented education.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eStart applying now to available programs at German universities: \u003ca href=\"https://www.educations.com/highlights/study-in-germany?utm_source=for9a\u0026utm_medium=paid+partner\u0026utm_campaign=Channel+Partner-2026+Study+in+Germany+School+Campaign+Q2\u0026utm_id=Channel+Partner-2026+Study+in+Germany+School+Campaign+Q2\"\u003ea wide range of options to suit different fields of study.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                },
                                {
                                    "header":  "Benefits",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"2946\" data-start=\"2876\"\u003eProgram structures vary by university and field but generally include:\u003c/p\u003e\u003col class=\"kh\" data-end=\"3075\" data-start=\"2947\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2966\" data-section-id=\"1a2n82q\" data-start=\"2947\"\u003eAcademic lectures\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3004\" data-section-id=\"1qk8r0r\" data-start=\"2967\"\u003ePractical projects and case studies\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3041\" data-section-id=\"14aqt7f\" data-start=\"3005\"\u003eInternships (in selected programs)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3075\" data-section-id=\"be9xeb\" data-start=\"3042\"\u003eTeam-based and applied learning\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"3138\" data-start=\"3077\"\u003ePrograms emphasize real-world skills and hands-on experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                },
                                {
                                    "header":  "Eligibility criteria",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003col class=\"kh\" data-end=\"2550\" data-start=\"2303\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2377\" data-section-id=\"6ni667\" data-start=\"2303\"\u003eHigh school diploma (for Bachelor\u0026rsquo;s) or Bachelor\u0026rsquo;s degree (for Master\u0026rsquo;s)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2443\" data-section-id=\"1n4ksvs\" data-start=\"2378\"\u003eProof of English proficiency (IELTS/TOEFL depending on program)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2501\" data-section-id=\"1w04cl2\" data-start=\"2444\"\u003eMeet specific admission requirements of each university\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2550\" data-section-id=\"17jku6g\" data-start=\"2502\"\u003eSubmit all required documents before deadlines\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                }
